    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to be impressed by this absolute showstopper! This vehicle is in pristine, mint condition and truly looks like it just left the dealership. Every inch of this car has been meticulously cared for, featuring a flawless exterior and an interior that still smells brand new. It's a rare find for anyone seeking perfection and a worry-free driving experience!",
